---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About — Mary Jane's Place"
  description="Built by a patient, for patients. Mary Jane's Place is a safe space in Bournemouth where medical cannabis patients are treated as patients."
>
  <section class="ph-top pad">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">About</div>
      <h1 class="rv">Built by a patient, for patients.</h1>
      <p class="rv lede" style="margin-top:16px">
        Mary Jane's Place began with one experience: being asked to leave a venue for
        using a legal, prescribed medicine. So we built somewhere that won't happen.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap two">
      <div class="rv">
        <h2 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:12px">Our story</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:13px">
          Our founder is a medical cannabis patient. After being treated as a criminal
          for taking medicine prescribed by a specialist, they decided patients deserved
          a proper welcome, not grudging tolerance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mary Jane's Place is the result: a calm space in Bournemouth where patients
          can use their medicine, ask questions, try equipment, and meet other people
          who understand it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv">
        <h2 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:12px">What we stand for</h2>
        <ul class="checks">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg>
            <span><b>No judgment.</b> Patients are treated as patients — full stop.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg>
            <span><b>Lawful and transparent.</b> Prescriptions verified, vaporisers only, nothing supplied.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg>
            <span><b>Discreet and inclusive.</b> A space designed for dignity and accessibility.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 6"/></svg>
            <span><b>Genuinely informative.</b> Good information and proper legal guidance are part of the service.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="band rv">
        <div class="narrow center" style="margin:0 auto">
          <div class="eyebrow">Our mission</div>
          <p style="font-size:clamp(19px,2.6vw,24px);line-height:1.5;color:#fff;margin-top:12px;font-weight:600">
            To give medical cannabis patients a safe place to use their medicine, and
            the clear information and support to do so with confidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pad-sm" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap two vc">
      <div class="rv">
        <h2 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:11px">More than a lounge</h2>
        <p>
          We host education evenings, device demonstrations, and informal peer support.
          Much of what we do is making sure patients leave knowing more than when they
          arrived — about their medicine, their options, and their rights.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rv card">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:8px">A growing model</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15.5px">
          The UK private medical cannabis market is worth an estimated £300–500m and growing
          ~10% a year, yet dedicated patient spaces remain rare. Mary Jane's Place is
          designed to be a credible, compliant model that can be repeated in other towns
          and cities — a network, not a chain.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
